It's almost double when you get
to the nineteenth-century bow.

00:11:11.679 --> 00:11:12.740
So the bow is bigger.
 

00:11:12.740 --> 00:11:14.399
So the whole thing is more
powerful,

00:11:14.399 --> 00:11:16.769
