00:12:24.476 --> 00:12:27.567
Symphony,"
number six, the Beethoven storm

00:12:27.567 --> 00:12:28.240
scene.
 

00:12:28.240 --> 00:12:30.871
If you wanted to get a sense of
the whistling wind up there,

00:12:30.871 --> 00:12:31.808
that's what he did.
 

00:12:31.808 --> 00:12:33.590
He had the piccolo play way,
way up high.

00:12:33.590 --> 00:12:34.840
Then you could hear it.
 

00:12:34.840 --> 00:12:36.220
It just kind of gave that
effect.

00:12:36.220 --> 00:12:39.470
At the other end there of the
